{
  "stem": "3150.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She also went to the DP camp, but she didn't stay with us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, it was normal.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, it was two years, almost two years.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] It was very normal.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You went to school.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we did some black market, you know, if you wanted a little luxury.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Which I was arrested, so one weekend I stayed in jail in--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--in Frankfurt, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, we, we smuggled some, believe it or not, it's schmaltz, some fat, you know, from, from Munich to Frankfurt.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was very-- so I used to do it on the weekends.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was picked up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We bought it in-- we bought it where we were.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we used to go on the train and go to Frankfurt.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sell it, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was more expensive there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And also salami, this type.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was, you know, to get some luxuries, and-- so one weekend, I, I, I was picked up.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was with another guy, but I was the only guy picked up, because they just like, you know-- and I spent July 4th weekend in a, in a Frankfurt jail, which was not very pleasant, by the way.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, that's, that's the point.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not as a Jew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was just black market, yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jail was terrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, I think that's the only time I've ever spent a day, but it's a two by four.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was with another person there, and I got stuck with July 4th weekend.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The way I got released is they really took me to, to American, not, not to German court.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I really gave them some story, which really made no sense, and the guy really couldn't care less, and he dismissed the case, you know.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They-- just about getting [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
